<section id='DefaultColorset'>
<title>DefaultColorset</title>

<cmdsynopsis>
	<command>DefaultColorset</command
	><arg choice='opt'
		><replaceable>num</replaceable
	></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>

<para><emphasis remap='B'>DefaultColorset</emphasis>
sets the colorset used by the windows controlled by the
<fvwmref cmd="DefaultColors"/>
command.  To revert back to the
<fvwmref cmd="DefaultColors"/>
colors use</para>

<programlisting>
DefaultColorset -1
</programlisting>

<para>or any variant of the
<fvwmref cmd="DefaultColors"/>
command.</para>

</section>
